<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٨٠٣ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2594">‌أَبُو دَاوُدَ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">‌شُعْبَةُ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4822">‌عَمْرٍو </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1091">‌جَابِرٍ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«كُنَّا نَعْزِلُ عَلَى عَهْدِ رَسُولِ اللهِ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ وَالْقُرْآنُ يَنْزِلُ عَلَيْهِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٧٣⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">فَقُلْتُ:</span> أَنْتَ سَمِعْتَهُ مِنْ جَابِرٍ؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> لَا».<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>